stay up late.

07:49.135 --> 07:52.096
It's like, all of a sudden,
I can't sleep without him, you know?

07:52.930 --> 07:53.931
I do.

07:54.599 --> 07:56.809
- What's your boyfriend's name?
- Eric.

07:57.435 --> 07:58.519
Eric Llewyn.

08:02.064 --> 08:03.441
Have you told him what happened?

08:03.733 --> 08:04.733
Mm-mm.

08:05.318 --> 08:07.487
