08:09.363 --> 08:11.824
No parents? No friends?

08:11.908 --> 08:12.909
Just you.

08:12.992 --> 08:14.577
I mean, 911.

08:16.329 --> 08:17.329
Is that weird?

08:18.331 --> 08:20.082
- No.
- Just, the thing is, um...

08:20.458 --> 08:22.210
