09:04.126 --> 09:06.587
I saw a guy walking around
the complex last night.

09:06.671 --> 09:09.382
Stocky, cowboy boots.
Never seen him before.

09:10.758 --> 09:13.511
There's a guy who lives here
I always thought was shady.

09:13.594 --> 09:14.929
Walks around with a headlamp on.

09:23.729 --> 09:24.729
How's the door?

09:24.981 --> 09:26.357
Flimsy.

09:28.192 --> 09:30.403
I'm just trying to think
if I left anything out.

09:30.653 --> 09:31.654
Take your time.

09:36.659 --> 09:37.659
Um...

09:38.452 --> 09:40.288
yeah. No, I...

09:41.497 --> 09:42.832
I think that's everything.

09:43.916 --> 09:46.502
And once you realized he was gone,
what'd you do then?

09:46.586 --> 09:47.712
I called 911.

09:48.754 --> 09:52.133
- Even though he told you not to?
- Well, yeah. I mean, of course.

09:54.218 --> 09:57.096
- Do you know roughly what time it was?
- 12:32.

09:58.055 --> 10:01.058
I... I checked.
I, um, I figured it mattered.

10:01.976 --> 10:03.102
You're right. It does.

10:08.190 --> 10:10.026
This is very helpful, Amber.

10:10.735 --> 10:13.821
The level of detail you're able
to remember gives me a lot to work with.

10:13.904 --> 10:15.281
- Thank you for that.
- Sure.

10:18.451 --> 10:21.746
