from your face now?

10:46.354 --> 10:47.354
Yeah.

10:47.563 --> 10:50.858
But like I said, he made me shower
and wash my face.

10:50.941 --> 10:54.028
I... I understand.
Still, I'd like to check.

10:54.612 --> 10:55.738
Okay.

11:37.988 --> 11:38.988
Okay.

11:39.990 --> 11:41.158
Thank you.

11:47.456 --> 11:49.875
