13:29.475 --> 13:30.893
So, he covered you,

13:31.769 --> 13:32.895
so you'd be warm?

13:32.978 --> 13:34.188
Yeah. And, um...

13:35.064 --> 13:38.567
like, when he left, he... he told me
to put a dowel in my sliding door

13:38.651 --> 13:40.569
